metadata.name: Mandatory invitation #1
metadata.description:
Episode 1
Mandatory invitation

Pepe was sitting at the bar when someone came up to him. This person handed him an envelope and went to the bathroom. Inside the envelope was a high-end chip. Pepe chased after the man to find out what this chip was. The man was not in the toilet. Could this chip have come from the clan his father was in? Could Pepe get into trouble like his father?

1- Pepe presses the button on the chip and activates the hologram.
2-Pepe throws the chip in the toilet and flushes it.
3-Pepe puts the chip in his pocket and goes home.

Don't forget to add the number of the option you want to choose to the last digit of your offer. Welcome to the game.

Big Credit to Matt Furie
Big Credit to Trystan
